    "10": "The night brings teeth, claws, and worse. I should prepare a weapon that keeps danger at a distance.",
    "20": "I have made a bow and arrows. Now I must prove I can hold the camp through the night.",
    "30": "The camp survived the dark. I am beginning to understand the patience and caution of the survivalist path."
  },
